ately marking covered methods. The JaCoCo report indicates methods are covered, but dynamic coverage is failing due to missing line numbers. Maybe the tests need assertions at call sites. I wonder if dynamic calls are logged without proper access. It's possible the dynamic report wasn't regenerated after the tests, or maybe the report generation failed. I'll check if the report only considers test methods and not library methods under certain conditions.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Reviewing test modifications**\\n\\nI want to add a tracking test to check internal nested object reads and writes, similar to BCElGamalPublicKey. This shouldn't cause any harm. Currently, deserialization is still blocked, so all tests are failing. Maybe they will pass after metadata is generated. I should also avoid having long lines that exceed 100 characters due to checkstyle enforcement. I can make adjustments and edit with tracking imports and assertions. \\n\\nI'll create a new test to confirm serialized key processes correctly and ensure that the output and input contain expected values.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_1HKldqOOJnSBv6Px3NKHjebb|fc_00c5cc8b9a72fe1d016a25fcc067a8819393c211227a2febf8", "name": "edit", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.bouncycastle/bcprov-jdk15to18/1.77/src/test/java/org_bouncycastle/bcprov_jdk15to18/JCEElGamalPrivateKeyTest.java", "edits": [{"oldText": "import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;\n\nimport java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\n", "newText": "import static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals;\nimport static org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertTrue;\n\nimport java.io.ByteArrayInputStream;\n"}, {"oldText": "import java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.math.BigInteger;\n\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.JCEElGamalPrivateKey;\n", "newText": "import java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.math.BigInteger;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.List;\n\nimport org.bouncycastle.jce.provider.JCEElGamalPrivateKey;\n"}, {"oldText": "    @Test\n    void javaSerializationWritesElGamalPrivateKeyParameters() throws Exception {\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey privateKey = deserialize(initialSerializedKey());\n\n        byte[] serialized = serialize(privateKey);\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey restored = deserialize(serialized);\n\n        assertElGamalPrivateKey(restored);\n        assertArrayEquals(privateKey.getEncoded(), restored.getEncoded());\n    }\n\n    private static void assertElGamalPrivateKey(JCEElGamalPrivateKey privateKey) {\n", "newText": "    @Test\n    void javaSerializationWritesElGamalPrivateKeyParameters() throws Exception {\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey privateKey = deserialize(initialSerializedKey());\n\n        byte[] serialized = serialize(privateKey);\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey restored = deserialize(serialized);\n\n        assertElGamalPrivateKey(restored);\n        assertArrayEquals(privateKey.getEncoded(), restored.getEncoded());\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void javaSerializationProcessesElGamalPrivateKeyParameterObjects() throws Exception {\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey privateKey = deserialize(initialSerializedKey());\n\n        TrackingObjectOutputStream outputStream = new TrackingObjectOutputStream();\n        outputStream.writeObject(privateKey);\n        outputStream.close();\n\n        TrackingObjectInputStream inputStream = new TrackingObjectInputStream(outputStream.toByteArray());\n        JCEElGamalPrivateKey restored = (JCEElGamalPrivateKey)inputStream.readObject();\n        inputStream.close();\n\n        assertElGamalPrivateKey(restored);\n        assertTrue(outputStream.bigIntegers.contains(X));\n        assertTrue(outputStream.bigIntegers.contains(P));\n        assertTrue(outputStream.bigIntegers.contains(G));\n        assertTrue(inputStream.bigIntegers.contains(X));\n        assertTrue(inputStream.bigIntegers.contains(P));\n        assertTrue(inputStream.bigIntegers.contains(G));\n    }\n\n    private static void assertElGamalPrivateKey(JCEElGamalPrivateKey privateKey) {\n"}, {"oldText": "        private JCEElGamalPrivateKeyObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream) throws IOException {\n            super(outputStream);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n", "newText": "        private JCEElGamalPrivateKeyObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream outputStream) throws IOException {\n            super(outputStream);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n"}, {"oldText": "            super.writeClassDescriptor(descriptor);\n        }\n    }\n}\n", "newText": "            super.writeClassDescriptor(descriptor);\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class TrackingObjectOutputStream extends ObjectOutputStream {\n        private final ByteArrayOutputStream byteOutputStream;\n        private final List<BigInteger> bigIntegers = new ArrayList<>();\n\n        private TrackingObjectOutputStream() throws IOException {\n            this(new ByteArrayOutputStream());\n        }\n\n        private TrackingObjectOutputStream(ByteArrayOutputStream byteOutputStream) throws IOException {\n            super(byteOutputStream);\n            this.byteOutputStream = byteOutputStream;\n            enableReplaceObject(true);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Object replaceObject(Object object) {\n            if (object instanceof BigInteger) {\n                bigIntegers.add((BigInteger)object);\n            }\n            return object;\n        }\n\n        private byte[] toByteArray() {\n            return byteOutputStream.toByteArray();\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static final class TrackingObjectInputStream extends ObjectInputStream {\n        private final List<BigInteger> bigIntegers = new ArrayList<>();\n\n        private TrackingObjectInputStream(byte[] serialized) throws IOException {\n            super(new ByteArrayInputStream(serialized));\n            enableResolveObject(true);\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected Object resolveObject(Object obje